FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773034803
OL,3,CStarmer to reassure public as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict enters tenth day
OL,6,FAfter Iran's supreme leader was killed
OL,7,Fin an Israeli strike at the start of
OL,8,Fthe war, his son Mojtaba Khamenei was
OL,9,Fnamed as his successor on Sunday, in a
OL,10,Fmove likely to draw the ire of US
OL,11,FPresident Donald Trump, who has
OL,12,Fpreviously said he would be an
OL,13,F"unacceptable" pick.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773034803
OL,3,CStarmer to reassure public as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict enters tenth day
OL,6,FEarlier, Sir Keir spoke to Mr Trump on
OL,7,Fthe phone about the countries'
OL,8,Fmilitary co-operation in the region,
OL,9,Fin what appeared to be a positive
OL,10,Fsignal a day after the US president
OL,11,Flashed out at him in a social media
OL,12,Fpost and suggested the UK's help was
OL,13,Ftoo late.
OL,15,FMr Trump has repeatedly hit out at Sir
OL,16,FKeir's decision not to grant
OL,17,Fpermission for the first wave of
OL,18,Fmilitary action against Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773034803
OL,3,CStarmer to reassure public as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict enters tenth day
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister later granted
OL,7,Fpermission for "defensive" US action
OL,8,Fagainst Iranian missile sites from UK
OL,9,Fbases, and four American bombers
OL,10,Flanded at RAF Fairford in
OL,11,FGloucestershire and the US started
OL,12,Fusing British bases for "specific
OL,13,Fdefensive operations".
OL,15,FAfter reports the UK was preparing the
OL,16,FHMS Prince of Wales aircraft carrier
OL,17,Fto go to the Middle East, Mr Trump
OL,18,Fsaid "we don't need them any longer"
OL,19,Fand that "we don't need people that
OL,20,Fjoin Wars after we've already won!".
OL,26,@oD@POUoD@ZO]tD@YOUuD@UO]zD@FOUzD@dO]{D@
OL,26,AJOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773034803
OL,3,CStarmer to reassure public as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict enters tenth day
OL,6,FNo decisions have yet been taken to
OL,7,Fdeploy the warship.
OL,9,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper had
OL,10,Fearlier defended Sir Keir, saying he
OL,11,Fis "right to stand up for Britain and
OL,12,FBritain's interests" and that the UK
OL,13,Fneeds to "take decisions ourselves"
OL,14,Fand should not be "outsourcing our
OL,15,Fpolicy to foreign countries".
OL,17,FShe also dismissed criticism from Sir
OL,18,FTony Blair, who had told a private
OL,19,Fevent that the UK "should have backed
OL,20,FAmerica from the beginning".
OL,26,@sD@DOUtD@TO]uD@JOUuD@cO]vD@SOUwD@\O]{D@
OL,26,ASOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773034803
OL,3,CStarmer to reassure public as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict enters tenth day
OL,6,F"Having been a minister in the last
OL,7,FLabour government, I also think it is
OL,8,Fimportant to learn lessons from what
OL,9,Fwent wrong in Iraq," she said.
OL,11,FSir Keir has sought to play down the
OL,12,Frift with the US, saying earlier this
OL,13,Fweek that the special relationship is
OL,14,F"in operation right now" as the two
OL,15,Fcountries share intelligence and work
OL,16,Ftogether amid the Middle East conflict.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@TO]vD@AOUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773034803
OL,3,CStarmer to reassure public as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict enters tenth day
OL,6,FLib Dem leader Sir Ed Davey has urged
OL,7,Fthe Prime Minister to call off the
OL,8,FKing's state visit to the US over Mr
OL,9,FTrump's "illegal war" and as the US
OL,10,Fleader "repeatedly insults and damages
OL,11,Four country".
OL,13,FMeanwhile, UK forces engaged an attack
OL,14,Fdrone fired from Iran to Iraq as RAF
OL,15,FTyphoons and F-35 jets conduct
OL,16,Fdefensive sorties across the region.
OL,18,FAnd a Merlin helicopter that can fly
OL,19,Fup to a mile in height and give
OL,20,Fadvance warning of incoming drones or
OL,21,Fmissiles is due to join.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@UO]rD@HOUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773034803
OL,3,CStarmer to reassure public as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict enters tenth day
OL,6,FA third Government charter flight to
OL,7,Fbring Britons home from the region was
OL,8,Fdue to leave Muscat, Oman, on Sunday
OL,9,Fjust before 7pm UK time and there are
OL,10,Fplans to charter a commercial flight
OL,11,Ffrom Dubai early this week.
OL,13,FMore than 32,000 British nationals
OL,14,Fhave now left the region, which
OL,15,Fincludes the Gulf countries as well as
OL,16,FIsrael and Lebanon, by air since March
OL,17,F1.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
